social_posts.post_text: Many challenges this year, but I feel like I came out on top!! Learned a lot about myself and what I’m capable of doing. I toured from February to October, all over the world, and some places more than once lol. I have @ajrbrothers and @thelumineers to thank for that (thank you). I will never fully feel like I deserve to be in the place that I’m in, but I am. And I’m so thankful because I know thousands would kill to be in my position. I think about that every day. My dream started a long time ago when I sat in my bed watching @reelbearmedia tour docs, and I told myself that is exactly what I was going to do one day. My heart is full!! I feel good about where my future is headed. I’m really excited.

I’ve been watching (and recording) the guys write the next chapter of their lives for quite some time now. It’s been really emotional to say the least. I’ve spent so much time with this family and I’m so honored to know and love them. We shot this video yesterday at the hospital, and I ran home as fast as possible to work on it. I’m sure everyone has had an emotional reaction to it, as I also did when they first played it for me. The support you guys have shown for the them has been really incredible. I know it means a lot to them (it means a lot to me too). Full video is on their YouTube channel.
